 1→# Plan 08: Renderer Switching
 2→
 3→## Problem
 4→
 5→The `renderer` prop exists on both `<OrbScene>` and `<Orb>` but does nothing. Need a system to select between CSS, Canvas, and WebGL renderers at runtime.
 6→
 7→## Design
 8→
 9→### Selection Hierarchy
10→
11→```text
12→Per-orb renderer prop > Scene renderer prop > Auto-detection
13→```
14→
15→1. If `<Orb renderer="webgl">` is set, use WebGL for that orb
16→2. If `<OrbScene renderer="canvas">` is set, use Canvas for all orbs (unless overridden)
17→3. If neither is set, auto-detect: WebGL > Canvas > CSS
18→
19→### Auto-Detection
20→
21→```typescript
22→let cachedRenderer: RendererType | null = null;
23→
24→function detectBestRenderer(): RendererType {
25→  if (cachedRenderer) return cachedRenderer;
26→
27→  if (typeof document === 'undefined') {
28→    // Don't cache SSR result — the module may later run in the browser
29→    return 'css';
30→  }
31→
32→  // Try WebGL
33→  const testCanvas = document.createElement('canvas');
34→  const gl = testCanvas.getContext('webgl2') || testCanvas.getContext('webgl');
35→  if (gl) {
36→    cachedRenderer = 'webgl';
37→    return cachedRenderer;
38→  }
39→
40→  // Try Canvas
41→  const ctx = testCanvas.getContext('2d');
42→  if (ctx) {
43→    cachedRenderer = 'canvas';
44→    return cachedRenderer;
45→  }
46→
47→  // Fallback
48→  cachedRenderer = 'css';
49→  return cachedRenderer;
50→}
51→```
52→
53→### Rendering Strategy per Renderer
54→
55→| Renderer | DOM Structure | Animation | Grain |
56→|----------|--------------|-----------|-------|
57→| CSS | N `<div>` elements per orb | CSS `@keyframes` | Separate `<canvas>` |
58→| Canvas | 1 `<canvas>` for all orbs | requestAnimationFrame | Same canvas |
59→| WebGL | 1 `<canvas>` for all orbs | requestAnimationFrame (shader uniforms) | Same shader |
60→

 65→- **Download** — JSON file export
 66→
 67→## Component Architecture
 68→
 69→```text
 70→@orbkit/editor
 71→  src/
 72→    index.ts                    — public exports
 73→    orb-editor.tsx              — main editor component
 74→    components/
 75→      preset-gallery.tsx        — preset thumbnails + randomize
 76→      canvas-preview.tsx        — live preview with draggable handles
 77→      orb-list.tsx              — orb selection list
 78→      orb-controls.tsx          — color/size/blur/blend controls for selected orb
 79→      scene-controls.tsx        — background/saturation/grain/breathing
 80→      export-panel.tsx          — copy JSX/JSON/CSS buttons
 81→    hooks/
 82→      use-editor-state.ts       — central state management (reducer)
 83→      use-drag.ts               — drag interaction for canvas handles
 84→      use-color-picker.ts       — color picker state
 85→    utils/
 86→      export-jsx.ts             — generate JSX string from config
 87→      export-json.ts            — serialize config
 88→      export-css.ts             — generate raw CSS
 89→      random-theme.ts           — randomize orb configuration
 90→    types.ts                    — editor-specific types
 91→```
 92→
 93→### State Management
 94→
 95→Use `useReducer` for predictable state updates:
 96→
 97→```typescript
 98→interface EditorState {
 99→  background: string;
100→  saturation: number;
101→  grain: number;
102→  breathing: number;
103→  orbs: EditorOrb[];
104→  selectedOrbId: string | null;
105→  renderer: RendererType;
106→}
107→
108→interface EditorOrb {
109→  id: string;
110→  color: string;
111→  position: Point;
112→  size: number;
113→  blur: number;
114→  blendMode: BlendMode;
115→}
116→
